Package: escalatoR
Type: Package
Title: DoD Cost Escalation Analysis Following CAPE Methodology
Version: 1.0.0
Date: 2024-01-15
Authors@R: c(
    person("Kevin", "Joy", email = "kevin.joy@example.com", role = c("aut", "cre")),
    person("Herren Associates", role = "cph"))
Description: Comprehensive system for Department of Defense (DoD) cost escalation 
    analysis following Cost Analysis and Program Evaluation (CAPE) methodology. 
    Provides tools for retrieving Producer Price Index data from FRED, calculating 
    escalation rates, generating forecasts, and creating weighted indices for 
    complex acquisition portfolios. Includes an interactive Shiny application 
    for guided analysis workflows.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
URL: https://github.com/frankij11/escalatoR
